----field----
field: {AA7CE48D-746C-42C7-BD64-9A51F7F10B7C}
name: Usage
key: usage
content-length: 717

<p>The screenshot above shows the Presentation Details for this page. In this case, you'll note that we are using the Main <a href="%7E/link.aspx?_id=431DD81B22CD4994B6220E2773818AC1&amp;_z=z">layout</a>, with various components for banners, menus, and display of terms.</p>
<p>An <a href="%7E/link.aspx?_id=B8FDADB4A041427DBB0E70C15ACA4379&amp;_z=z">item </a>can exist in Sitecore without having presentation details (examples include metadata, settings, content which flows into components). Presentation Details can also be applied to a template <a href="%7E/link.aspx?_id=2BF103381CFF4F9F890EE9F3078473F9&amp;_z=z">standard values</a>, meaning that any new item created, inherits those settings automatically.</p>
